models.gridobjects.items

Class Tree

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.gridobjects.GridObject
      • models.gridobjects.items.Item
        • models.gridobjects.items.Tree
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Tree
extends Item
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Tree object extends Item and acts as an obstruction inside the grid. The Tree allows for Eve to climb into it, move to a neighboring tree, store bamboo and take bamboo from the tree.
    Author:
    Carmine Iannaccone
